  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Confront demonic invaders across Planet Earth as you fight for survival. Level up your survivor, collect an arsenal of unfathomable firepower, and discover your true potential as you fight your way across your homeworld in this thrilling, action packed first person combat experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/97fdc51369ff1a1551bfff8f465e68a2.poster.avif?t=1745866444\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/97fdc51369ff1a1551bfff8f465e68a2.webm?t=1745866444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/97fdc51369ff1a1551bfff8f465e68a2.mp4?t=1745866444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BECOME THE ULTIMATE SURVIVOR</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight for survival like no human ever has. Unleash powerful Abilities, and wield a vast array of destructive weaponry to eliminate hordes of demons on sight. And after all the dust clears, earn powerful, unique rewards, allowing you to return to the battlefield to unleash Mayhem however you please.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/d0fea5777357ae4c85cebb42c9b2a5bf.poster.avif?t=1745866444\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/d0fea5777357ae4c85cebb42c9b2a5bf.webm?t=1745866444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/d0fea5777357ae4c85cebb42c9b2a5bf.mp4?t=1745866444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE ALONGSIDE FRIENDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a Squad with friends and obtain valuable bonus Rewards upon surviving Missions together through teamwork promoting, co-op gameplay. Discover ways to empower allies, misdirect your enemies, and complete your objectives. Finding the demons too daunting on a certain mission? There is in game matchmaking so you can connect with friendly Survivors whenever you need assistance.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/0b7c333a1e4ca4b34cdc6af6b8382504.poster.avif?t=1745866444\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/0b7c333a1e4ca4b34cdc6af6b8382504.webm?t=1745866444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/0b7c333a1e4ca4b34cdc6af6b8382504.mp4?t=1745866444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPERIENCE AN EPIC STORY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the pre apocalypse of Earth, to the aftermath, experience a massive series of Co-op Campaign Missions as you are guided by a high tech military Artificial Intelligence. Unleash your true power within, as you experience a survival situation unlike any other with a Combat Archetype of your choice, hone your survival skills, and ultimately prevent the extinction of humanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/27cdb0bc50b2def6505526aa810d40ce.poster.avif?t=1745866444\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/27cdb0bc50b2def6505526aa810d40ce.webm?t=1745866444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/27cdb0bc50b2def6505526aa810d40ce.mp4?t=1745866444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MASTER YOUR ARSENAL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your starting Guns are just the beginning. Craft hundreds of destructive weapons of all kinds, plus Companions and more. Level up and experiment until you find the right combination of equipment that suits your unique playstyle. Paint your weaponry as you please to compliment your custom-designed loadout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/1e0e1ccb618b1a2ee1491a0e36f10c15.poster.avif?t=1745866444\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/1e0e1ccb618b1a2ee1491a0e36f10c15.webm?t=1745866444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/1e0e1ccb618b1a2ee1491a0e36f10c15.mp4?t=1745866444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CUSTOMIZE NON-STOP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Entering the Earth Last Stand Force means joining platoons of friendly Survivors, each with their own personalized Uniforms, Weapons and gear. With a staggering number of Customization options available to upgrade your Loadout, designing the perfect look for your Survivor makes for an endlessly rewarding challenge for you and your Squad. </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Confront demonic invaders across Planet Earth as you fight for survival. Level up your survivor, collect an arsenal of unfathomable firepower, and discover your true potential as you fight your way across your homeworld in this thrilling, action packed first person combat experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/97fdc51369ff1a1551bfff8f465e68a2.poster.avif?t=1745866444\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/97fdc51369ff1a1551bfff8f465e68a2.webm?t=1745866444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/97fdc51369ff1a1551bfff8f465e68a2.mp4?t=1745866444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BECOME THE ULTIMATE SURVIVOR</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight for survival like no human ever has. Unleash powerful Abilities, and wield a vast array of destructive weaponry to eliminate hordes of demons on sight. And after all the dust clears, earn powerful, unique rewards, allowing you to return to the battlefield to unleash Mayhem however you please.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/d0fea5777357ae4c85cebb42c9b2a5bf.poster.avif?t=1745866444\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/d0fea5777357ae4c85cebb42c9b2a5bf.webm?t=1745866444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/d0fea5777357ae4c85cebb42c9b2a5bf.mp4?t=1745866444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE ALONGSIDE FRIENDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a Squad with friends and obtain valuable bonus Rewards upon surviving Missions together through teamwork promoting, co-op gameplay. Discover ways to empower allies, misdirect your enemies, and complete your objectives. Finding the demons too daunting on a certain mission? There is in game matchmaking so you can connect with friendly Survivors whenever you need assistance.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/0b7c333a1e4ca4b34cdc6af6b8382504.poster.avif?t=1745866444\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/0b7c333a1e4ca4b34cdc6af6b8382504.webm?t=1745866444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/0b7c333a1e4ca4b34cdc6af6b8382504.mp4?t=1745866444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPERIENCE AN EPIC STORY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the pre apocalypse of Earth, to the aftermath, experience a massive series of Co-op Campaign Missions as you are guided by a high tech military Artificial Intelligence. Unleash your true power within, as you experience a survival situation unlike any other with a Combat Archetype of your choice, hone your survival skills, and ultimately prevent the extinction of humanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051870/extras/27cdb0bc50b2def6505526aa810d40ce.poster.avif?t=1745866444\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.ak